prings in Iceland<\/a>.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7957&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/18150133\/iceland-travel-guide-1.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/18150133\/iceland-travel-guide-1-19x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/18150133\/iceland-travel-guide-1-376x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"Iceland Travel Guide: The Ultimate 2-week Trip\" height=\"600\" width=\"376\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>The last 70-minute drive is to the campsite at the Glj&#xFA;frafoss and Seljalandsfoss waterfall. The campsite is named Hamragar&#xF0;ar. Prepare your meal here and maybe even try to visit the Glj&#xFA;frafoss waterfall, which is hidden in between the rocks.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Today&#x2019;s drive: 3.5 hours<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image vertical-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/iceland-route-guide-hot-springs-Hrunalaug.jpg\" alt=\"iceland route guide hot springs Hrunalaug\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"iceland route guide hot springs Hrunalaug\" class=\"wp-image-8248 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152806\/iceland-route-guide-hot-springs-Hrunalaug.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152806\/iceland-route-guide-hot-springs-Hrunalaug-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152806\/iceland-route-guide-hot-springs-Hrunalaug-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152806\/iceland-route-guide-hot-springs-Hrunalaug-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152806\/iceland-route-guide-hot-springs-Hrunalaug-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152806\/iceland-route-guide-hot-springs-Hrunalaug-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152806\/iceland-route-guide-hot-springs-Hrunalaug-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152806\/iceland-route-guide-hot-springs-Hrunalaug-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152806\/iceland-route-guide-hot-springs-Hrunalaug-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152806\/iceland-route-guide-hot-springs-Hrunalaug-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152806\/iceland-route-guide-hot-springs-Hrunalaug-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.co