nd travel guide: Visiting Diamonds<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Rise and shine early. Hope you slept well? Make sure the check all of our tips for <a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/iceland\/camping-iceland\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Rise and shine early. Hope you slept well? Make sure the check all of our tips for camping in Iceland. (opens in a new tab)\">camping in Iceland<\/a>.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Our first stop is Diamond Beach. The black beach is filled with blocks of ice that have separated themselves from the glacier. On the other side of the road is the enormous J&#xF6;kurs&#xE1;l&#xF3;n Glacier Lagoon where you can take a boat tour and sail among the massive icebergs.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/iceland-route-guide-diamond-beach.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"8267\" class=\"wp-image-8267 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1484px) 100vw, 1484px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152725\/iceland-route-guide-diamond-beach.jpg 1484w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152725\/iceland-route-guide-diamond-beach-300x388.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152725\/iceland-route-guide-diamond-beach-600x776.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152725\/iceland-route-guide-diamond-beach-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152725\/iceland-route-guide-diamond-beach-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152725\/iceland-route-guide-diamond-beach-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152725\/iceland-route-guide-diamond-beach-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152725\/iceland-route-guide-diamond-beach-126x163.jpg 126w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152725\/iceland-route-guide-diamond-beach-139x180.jpg 139w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152725\/iceland-route-guide-diamond-beach-594x768.jpg 594w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152725\/iceland-route-guide-diamond-beach-791x1024.jpg 791w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152725\/iceland-route-guide-diamond-beach-835x1080.jpg 835w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152725\/iceland-route-guide-diamond-beach-1113x1440.jpg 1113w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152725\/iceland-route-guide-diamond-beach-23x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152725\/iceland-route-guide-diamond-beach.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure><\/li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/iceland-route-guide-glacier-lagoon.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"8268\" class=\"wp-image-8268 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-wi