r.com\/iceland\/hot-springs-iceland\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">hot springs in Iceland<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Spend the night around the Myvatn lake at one of the many campsites.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Today&#x2019;s drive: 4.5 hours<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/iceland-route-guide-Myvatn-Nature-Baths.jpg\" alt=\"iceland route guide Myvatn Nature Baths\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"iceland route guide Myvatn Nature Baths\" class=\"wp-image-8276 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152700\/iceland-route-guide-Myvatn-Nature-Baths.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152700\/iceland-route-guide-Myvatn-Nature-Baths-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152700\/iceland-route-guide-Myvatn-Nature-Baths-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152700\/iceland-route-guide-Myvatn-Nature-Baths-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152700\/iceland-route-guide-Myvatn-Nature-Baths-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152700\/iceland-route-guide-Myvatn-Nature-Baths-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152700\/iceland-route-guide-Myvatn-Nature-Baths-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152700\/iceland-route-guide-Myvatn-Nature-Baths-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152700\/iceland-route-guide-Myvatn-Nature-Baths-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/upload