saltinourhair.com\/iceland\/campsites-iceland\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">best campings in Iceland<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Today&#x2019;s drive: 2.5 hours<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/iceland-route-guide-scenic-church.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"8286\" class=\"wp-image-8286 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152631\/iceland-route-guide-scenic-church.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152631\/iceland-route-guide-scenic-church-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152631\/iceland-route-guide-scenic-church-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152631\/iceland-route-guide-scenic-church-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152631\/iceland-route-guide-scenic-church-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152631\/iceland-route-guide-scenic-church-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152631\/iceland-route-guide-scenic-church-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152631\/iceland-route-guide-scenic-church-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152631\/iceland-route-guide-scenic-church-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152631\/iceland-route-guide-scenic-church-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.salt