 Iceland&#x2019;s most photographed spots. It&#x2019;s best to visit it as early as possible or the night before (day 10) if you have good weather. The campsite is only 20 minutes away.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Also read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/iceland\/packing-list-iceland\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Packing List for Iceland in summer<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image vertical-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/iceland-route-guide-waterfalls-Kirkjufell.jpg\" alt=\"iceland route guide waterfalls Kirkjufell\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"iceland route guide waterfalls Kirkjufell\" class=\"wp-image-8289 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1484px) 100vw, 1484px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152626\/iceland-route-guide-waterfalls-Kirkjufell.jpg 1484w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152626\/iceland-route-guide-waterfalls-Kirkjufell-300x388.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152626\/iceland-route-guide-waterfalls-Kirkjufell-600x776.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152626\/iceland-route-guide-waterfalls-Kirkjufell-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152626\/iceland-route-guide-waterfalls-Kirkjufel