-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> Instead of staying in a hotel, go to the campsite just 8 minutes out of town.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<p>The next day, wake up and go to Braud &amp; Co, the best bakery in town. Followed by a visit to the Blue Lagoon. Get here as early or late as possible to avoid the crowds.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/iceland-route-guide-reykjavik-best-bakery.jpg\" alt=\"iceland route guide reykjavik best bakery\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"iceland route guide reykjavik best bakery\" class=\"wp-image-8301 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152602\/iceland-route-guide-reykjavik-best-bakery.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152602\/iceland-route-guide-reykjavik-best-bakery-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152602\/iceland-route-guide-reykjavik-best-bakery-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152602\/iceland-route-guide-reykjavik-best-bakery-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152602\/iceland-route-guide-reykjavik-best-bakery-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152602\/iceland-route-guide-reykjavik-best-bakery-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152602\/iceland-route-guide-reykjavik-best-bakery-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152602\/iceland-route-guide-reykjavik-best-bakery-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152602\/iceland-route-guide-reykjavik-best-bakery-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152602\/iceland-route-guide-reykjavik-best-bakery-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152602\/iceland-route-guide-reykjavik-best-bakery-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152602\/iceland-route-guide-reykjavik-best-bakery-1440x961.jpg 1440w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152602\/iceland-route-guide-reykjavik-best-bakery-30x20.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152602\/iceland-route-guide-reykjavik-best-bakery.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p><strong>Fun fact:<\/strong> Did you know Golfing in a very popular sport in Iceland?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Today is the day to return your campervan or rental car and maybe <a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/go\/base-iceland\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Today is the day to return your campervan or rental car and maybe sleep near the airport so you&#x2019;ll have a cheap shuttle. (opens in a new tab)\">sleep near the airport<\/a> so you&#x2019;ll have a cheap shuttle.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Today&#x2019;s drive: 1 hour<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Day 14: See you next time in Iceland!<\/h3>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"transport\">Getting around in Iceland<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<h3>Driving in Iceland<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The best way to explore Iceland is by car. The country is made for a road trip and your own car gives you the ultimate freedom to stop when and where ever you would like. Roads are well paved and the roads marked with an F are 4wd only. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-iceland\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Book a rental car<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image vertical-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/iceland-route-guide-driving-road.jpg\" alt=\"iceland route guide driving road\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"iceland route guide driving road\" class=\"wp-image-8305 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152559\/iceland-route-guide-driving-road.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152559\/iceland-route-guide-driving-road-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152559\/iceland-route-guide-driving-road-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152559\/iceland-route-guide-driving-road-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152559\/iceland-route-guide-driving-road-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152559\/iceland-route-guide-driving-road-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152559\/iceland-route-guide-