               <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                            <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/div>Transport Rental: 160 USD \/ day\n                    <\/li><li>\n                            <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                                <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                                <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <\/div>Camping: 25 USD \/ night<\/li><li>\n                            <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                                <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                                <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <\/div>Fuel: 80 USD \/ 40L Diesel<\/li><li>\n                            <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                                <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                                <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <\/div>Shower: 3 USD \/ day<\/li><li>\n                            <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                                <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                                <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <\/div>Van Wifi: 4 USD \/ day<\/li><\/ul><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"saving\">9 x Budget saving tips<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>There are a few good tricks to save a lot of money and travel on a budget in Iceland.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Shop at Bonus and Kronan<\/li><li>Shopping at gas stations is twice as expensive<\/li><li>Drink tap water<\/li><li>Don&#x2019;t do too many guided tours<\/li><li>Use a Happy Campers gas station discount pass<\/li><li>Skip drinking alcohol<\/li><li>Prepare pasta or rice only with vegetables and sauce. Meat in Iceland is expensive.<\/li><li>Don&#x2019;t eat every night at restaurants<\/li><li>Camp! Hotels are a budget killer<\/li><\/ol>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"besttime\">Best time to visit Iceland<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>July to August are Iceland&#x2019;s warmest months and almost the most popular time to visit Iceland. Keep in mind that in those months you don&#x2019;t have the northern lights because of the 24-hours of daylight.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>May and September are best all round to avoid the mass visitors and still have the chance for good weather.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/iceland-route-guide-camper-van.jpg\" alt=\"iceland route guide camper van\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"290\" alt=\"iceland route guide camper van\" class=\"wp-image-8309 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152547\/iceland-route-guide-camper-van.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152547\/iceland-route-guide-camper-van-300x193.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152547\/iceland-route-guide-camper-van-600x386.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152547\/iceland-route-guide-camper-van-450x290.jpg 450w, https:\